  "methods": "<p>This was a retrospective analysis. Serum samples were obtained from several biorepositories. The C<sub>18</sub> and C<sub>20</sub> lipoforms of G<sub>D2</sub> were measured in the serum samples using a validated HPLC/MS/MS assay</p>\r\n",
